{"tid":2368763,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"預算案｜鄉議局倡容許投注NBA","createTime":"2021-01-16T12:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T13:17:58.000Z","uid":241774,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c257b11aa50566a8d73fd2619d5b322caddeb842","tid":2368763,"uid":241774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"又幾貼地喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄉議局主席劉業強表示，政府推出多輪防疫抗疫基金後，財政儲備降至8,000多億元，應設法開源，擴闊稅基，增設與民生關係較少、對市民影響較輕的稅項，例如紅酒稅等，料每年可為庫房帶來數以億計收入，亦建議提高煙草稅、高碳排放汽車的首次登記稅等。劉業強建議，政府可容許市民投注NBA籃球賽和桌球等，增加政府的體育博彩稅收入。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE ：柒到加01"},{"pid":"1b4098a8ad3968d2b276e1ba2f1c1f22a349d321","tid":2368763,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:52:18.000Z","msg":"損害有錢人利益不了"},{"pid":"c4a4fb29a2825628ce8424af95259acd1dc39342","tid":2368763,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"港超"},{"pid":"82eb45436acea54b53d3bc07d83f1719d3531633","tid":2368763,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"不如用新界鄉區建賭場啦屌"},{"pid":"af14fc2bbdbb7024cef4c7617cab9e6150de83d5","tid":2368763,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"開放賭權啦"},{"pid":"bfef558fde575022156e760acf0ca94a026707f9","tid":2368763,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"開放公娼"},{"pid":"9aa6ffde8c0fe196e6cb43f9e35398dc2221c54d","tid":2368763,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82eb45436acea54b53d3bc07d83f1719d3531633","tid":2368763,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"不如用新界鄉區建賭場啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"建議唔錯<br /